##  TRAVEL & TOUR WEBSITE

Welcome to our Travel & Tour website! This platform is designed to help you explore the world, plan your vacations, and discover exciting travel packages. Our website features a variety of pages, including articles, an about section, services, a gallery, and a contact page, all built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

* Table of Contents
* Features
* Installation
* Usage
* Pages Overview
* Contributing
* License
* Features

# Dark Mode Toggle: Easily switch between light and dark themes for a comfortable browsing experience.

## Article Page: Read insightful travel articles with the option to toggle dark mode.

## About Page: Learn about our history and mission.

## Services Page:

- Countdown timer for discounts on travel packages.
- A form to purchase tickets.
- A to-do list for your travel preparations.
- Gallery: View beautiful images from various travel destinations.

## Contact Page:

- Send us messages or report problems through a contact form.
- Customer care support via phone and email.

## Installation
To get started with our Travel & Tour website, follow these steps:

## Clone the repository:
bash
- git clone https://github.com/yourusername/travel-tour-website.git  
- Navigate to the project directory:
bash
- cd travel-tour-website  
- Open the index.html file in your preferred web browser.

## Usage
- Dark Mode Toggle: Click the toggle button in the header to switch between light and dark modes.
- To-Do List: Add items to your travel checklist to ensure you don't forget anything important.
- Ticket Purchase: Fill out the ticket purchase form on the services page to book your travel packages.
- Contact Us: Use the contact form to send inquiries or report issues.
